#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.276"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.276:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.276:0.2"
msgid "28. Rāgapeyyāla"
msgstr "28. Abbreviated Texts Beginning with Greed"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: catuiddhipādasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.276:0.3"
msgid "276. Iddhipādasutta"
msgstr "276. Bases of Psychic Power"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.276:1.1"
msgid "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr "“For insight into greed, four things should be developed."

msgctxt "an4.276:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.276:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ "
"bhāveti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm, and active effort. "

msgctxt "an4.276:1.4"
msgid ""
"vīriyasamādhi … pe … cittasamādhi … pe … "
"vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr ""
"They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy … "
"mental development … inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "an4.276:1.5"
msgid "Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti."
msgstr "For insight into greed, these four things should be developed.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.276:1.6"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
